	 (N'Labour Statistics-Employment-Industrial Category-Agriculture',N'Labour Statistics',N'000 persons',N'',N'R',N'N',N'Q-A',0,N'Department of Census and Statistics',N'(a) Data up to 2010 are for the household population aged 10 years and above and data from 2011 onwards are for the household population aged 15 years and above
